      "kind": {
        "Brief": {
          "id": "theory",
          "title": "Theory:",
          "brief_html": "<p>Given $x \\equiv a_i \\pmod{n_i}$ with pairwise coprime moduli, CRT constructs the unique solution modulo $N = \\prod n_i$:</p>\n<p>$$x = \\sum a_i \\cdot N_i \\cdot \\text{invmod}(N_i, n_i) \\pmod N$$</p>\n<p>where $N_i = N / n_i$.</p>\n"
        }
      },
      "execution": {
